responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "3826D21C4911F5E0F96B8EB9409FDBE0", "The farm\'s been overrun with goblins! It\'s a lost cause if you ask me, the vermin are everywhere. I do have a plan, though, if one of stout heart and fiery temper could lend such to my assistance, we could merely extract the very elements that make this land so productive.Leave Daragal to the goblins, says I, and let us take what we need elsewhere! It won\'t be easy, though. The goblins\' meddling has roused ill-tempered spirits, and they keep the well. You will need to quiet the lesser lords of Daragal, then rouse their Taskmaster to gain access to the water.")
name: SQ_BL_Daragal_Rhondo_30
